  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in an iron teppan pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until charred, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced red pepper and cook for another 3 minutes.",
    "Add the saffron and smoked paprika, stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sweetcorn kernels, chicken broth, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer, then reduce the heat to low and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro and serve hot.",
    "Let the paella rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Break the paella into pieces and serve.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Serve with a dollop of sour cream or a sprinkle of queso fresco, if desired."
